WEBVTT

00:10:29.260 --> 00:10:31.307
In tudi če sprejmemo dramatične ukrepe

00:10:31.331 --> 00:10:34.696
in se izognemo nekaterim
resnično grozljivim scenarijem,

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:38.565
bi pomenilo živeti
na povsem drugem planetu.

00:10:39.193 --> 00:10:42.162
Z novo politiko, z novo ekonomijo,

00:10:42.186 --> 00:10:44.376
z novim odnosom do tehnologije

00:10:44.400 --> 00:10:46.709
in z novim odnosom do narave,

00:10:46.733 --> 00:10:49.462
cel nov svet.

00:10:50.336 --> 00:10:52.270
Ampak razmeroma dober za življenje

00:10:53.074 --> 00:10:54.860
Razmeroma uspešen.

00:10:55.987 --> 00:10:57.137
In zelen.

00:10:58.392 --> 00:11:00.587
Zakaj ne izberemo tega?